ldren":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/92/dB/tXXVIII/s2801"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–92, div. B, title XXVIII, § 2801","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2015-11-25"},"text":"Nov. 25, 2015","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/129/1168"},"text":"129 Stat. 1168","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idabc5be5f-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idabc5be60-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idabc5be61-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2015—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/92/s2801/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–92, § 2801(1)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “in excess of the amount specified in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2805/b/1"},"text":"section 2805(b)(1) of this title","children":[],"tail":"” for “in an amount in excess of $750,000” in introductory provisions."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b)(3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/92/s2801/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–92, § 2801(2)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “subsection (e) of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2811"},"text":"section 2811 of this title","children":[],"tail":") that costs less than the amount specified in subsection (d) of such section” for “"},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2811/e"},"text":"section 2811(e) of this title","children":[],"tail":") that costs less than $7,500,000”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2011—Subsec. (b)(2)(B)(ii). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/81"},"text":"Pub. L. 112–81","children":[],"tail":" substituted “section 2805(a)” for “section 2805(a)(2)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2004—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/375"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–375","children":[],"tail":" amended section generally, substituting provisions relating to notice and wait requirements for certain projects for provisions relating to limitation on certain projects and authority to carry out small projects with operation and maintenance funds."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2000—Subsec. (b)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/398/s1/dA"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–398, § 1 [[div. A]","children":[],"tail":", title X, § 1087(a)(22)(A)], substituted “section 2805(c)(1)(A)” for “section 2805(c)(1)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/398/s1/dA"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–398, § 1 [[div. A]","children":[],"tail":", title X, § 1087(a)(22)(B)], substituted “section 2805(c)(1)(B)” for “section 2805(c)(2)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1999—Subsec. (a)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/65/s1067/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–65, § 1067(1)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “and the Committee on Armed Services” for “and the Committee on National Security”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(2)(C). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/65/s2806/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–65, § 2806(a)","children":[],"tail":", added subpar. (C)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/65/s2806/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–65, § 2806(b)","children":[],"tail":", amended subsec. (b) generally. Prior to amendment, subsec. (b) read as follows: “Under such regulations as the Secretary of Defense may prescribe, a project authorized under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s18233/a"},"text":"section 18233(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":" that costs $500,000 or less may be carried out with funds available for operations and maintenance.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1996—Subsec. (a)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/201/s2801/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–201, § 2801(c)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “$1,500,000” for “$400,000”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/106"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–106","children":[],"tail":" substituted “the Committee on Armed Services and the Committee on Appropriations of the Senate and the Committee on National Security and the Committee on Appropriations of the” for “the Committees on Armed Services and on Appropriations of the Senate and”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/201/s2801/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–201, § 2801(b)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “$500,000” for “$300,000”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1994—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/337/s1664/b/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–337, § 1664(b)(2)","children":[],"tail":", renumbered "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2233a"},"text":"section 2233a of this title","children":[],"tail":" as this section."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/337/s1664/b/5/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–337, § 1664(b)(5)(A)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “18233” for “2233”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/337/s1664/b/5/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–337, § 1664(b)(5)(B)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “18233(a)” for “2233(a)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1991—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/190"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–190","children":[],"tail":" substituted “$300,000” for “$200,000”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1987—Subsec. (a)(2)(B)(ii)(II). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/26"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–26","children":[],"tail":" substituted “specified by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2805/a/2"},"text":"section 2805(a)(2) of this title","children":[],"tail":"” for “specified by law”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/180"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–180","children":[],"tail":" substituted “$200,000” for “$100,000”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1984—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/407"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–407","children":[],"tail":" substituted “$100,000” for “$50,000”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1983—Subsec. (a)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/115"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–115","children":[],"tail":" substituted “$400,000” for “$200,000”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1982—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/214"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–214","children":[],"tail":" substituted “Limitation on certain projects; authority to carry out small projects with operation and maintenance funds” for “Limitation” as section catchline and completely revised text. Before such revision section had provided that no expenditure or contribution of more than $175,000 could be made under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2233"},"text":"section 2233 of this title","children":[],"tail":" for any facility until after the expiration of thirty days from the date upon which the Secretary of Defense or his designee notified the Senate and the House of Representatives of the location, nature, and estimated cost of such facility, but that such requirement did not apply to facilities acquired by lease, facilities acquired, constructed, expanded, rehabilitated, converted, or equipped to restore or replace facilities damaged or destroyed, where the Senate and the House of Representatives had been notified of that action, and that, under such regulations as the Secretary of Defense might prescribe, any project authorized pursuant to section 2233(a) which did not cost more than $50,000 could be accomplished from appropriations available for maintenance and operations."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1979—Par. (1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/125"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–125","children":[],"tail":" substituted “$175,000” for “$100,000”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1975—Par. (2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/107"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–107","children":[],"tail":" substituted “$50,000” for “$25,000”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1974—Par. (1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/552"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–552","children":[],"tail":" substituted “$100,000” for “$850,000”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1962—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/554"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–554","children":[],"tail":" designated existing provisions as par. (1), substituted “until after the expiration of thirty days from the date upon which the Secretary of Defense or his designee notifies the Senate and the House of Representatives of the location, nature, and estimated cost of such facility” for “that has not been authorized by a law authorizing appropriations for specific facilities for reserve forces”, and added par. (2)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idabc5be62-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"